# Multimodal Image Understanding and Hallucination Analysis

A multimodal AI pipeline that combines image captioning, visual question answering (VQA), and explanation generation using state-of-the-art Vision-Language Models. This project also investigates hallucination issues in multimodal systems by analyzing generated outputs against actual image content.

---

## Project Overview

This project integrates multiple pre-trained transformer models to perform image understanding and explanation generation.

### Models Used

| Model | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| BLIP | Image Captioning |
| BLIP-VQA | Visual Question Answering |
| FLAN-T5 | Explanation Generation |

The system takes an input image, generates a descriptive caption, answers image-related questions, and produces a detailed explanation.

